<document>
    <properties>
        <title>ironsites - Components &amp; Misc.</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <section name="ironsites Text">
            <p>
                This extension to the foundation text component supports HTML
                filtering based on a configurable 
                <a href="https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Category:OWASP_AntiSamy_Project#Stage_3_-_Tailoring_the_policy_file" target="_blank">anti-samy policy file</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section name="ironsites Sitemap">
            <p>
                In addition to showcasing the HidePageFilter, this extension 
                of the out-of-box sitemap offers more options. Additionally the
                components responds to XML extension which should meet a basic
                need to programmatically generate 
                <a href="http://sitemaps.org" target="_blank">sitemap.xml</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section name="ironsites Cache Monitor">
            <p>
                This component displays caching information while also
                making use of i18nHelper and modeHelper.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section name="ironsites Kitchen Sink">
            <p>
                Artificial examples of the available development utilities.
                Ultimately this component is not for practical use.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section name="Misc.">
            <p>
                Developers will find helpful methods in WCMUtil and XSSUtil.
            </p>
        </section>
    </body>
</document>